text: Wesam Malik (born 1 January 1989) is an Iraqi footballer who plays as a midfielder for Naft Al-Janoob in the Iraq Premier League, as well as the Iraq national team. ==International career== On 24 July 2016, Wesam made his first international cap with Iraq against Uzbekistan in a friendly match. == References == == External links == * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Association football midfielders Category:Iraqi footballers Category:Iraq international footballers Category:Naft Al-Janoob players
